Block attributes come before the block, on a line by themselves.
```
{#id}
A paragraph
.
<p id="id">A paragraph</p>
```

```
{.class}
A paragraph
.
<p class="class">A paragraph</p>
```

```
{.class #id}
A paragraph
.
<p class="class" id="id">A paragraph</p>
```

```
{.class=}
A paragraph
.
<p>{.class=}
A paragraph</p>
```

```
{.one .two .three}
A paragraph
.
<p class="one two three">A paragraph</p>
```


```
{.one.two.three}
A paragraph
.
<p>{.one.two.three}
A paragraph</p>
```

```
{#one #two #three}
A paragraph
.
<p id="three">A paragraph</p>
```


```
{#one#two#three}
A paragraph
.
<p>{#one#two#three}
A paragraph</p>
```
